How current APP works

4 components:
Header
Part
Content
Total

All components take props 

The component will build whats being displayed 

Header:
  returns  <h1> {props.course} </h1>
  here I passed props and a name in the h1 tag in my APP
  in header I call the header component and pass the course= {course}

Part:
  return  <p>{name} {exercise}</p>
  I pass name and excerise and in my content I call Part where I pass the 
  name and props.part's' and exercise= props.exercise's'

Content: 
  takes props I pass Part and then the name={parts} and exercise={excerise}

Total:
  takes props and i add all the props.excerises
